- The integer array parameter `weights` must not be null.
- The integer array parameter `weights` length is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100000.
- All values in the integer array parameter `weights` are greater than or equal to 1 and are less than or equal to 1000000000.
- The integer parameter `k` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to the length of the integer array parameter `weights`.
- The long result is the difference between the maximum and minimum scores among marble distributions.